      "parameters": {
        "mode": "retrieve-as-tool",
        "toolDescription": "This node connects to the Pinecone vector store where the Samsung \nCustomer Support Knowledge Base (Samsung_Customer_Support_QA.pdf) \nhas been indexed and embedded.\n\nWhen a customer asks a support question, this node converts the \nquestion into a vector embedding and searches the Pinecone index \nfor the most relevant document chunks — such as Q&A pairs, device \nspecs, troubleshooting steps, or warranty information.\n\nThe top matching chunks are returned as context and passed to the \nAI agent, which uses them to generate a precise, document-grounded \nresponse. Only information found in the knowledge base is used — \nthe bot does not answer from general knowledge.",
